THE MUSIC BECOMES

21:08.101 --> 21:11.812
MORE AND MORE FURIOUS,

21:11.854 --> 21:14.607
UNTIL FINALLY, TEMI...

21:14.648 --> 21:16.943
YOU PLAY THE SOLO.

