OKAY.

21:18.111 --> 21:19.612
ALL RIGHT!

21:18.111 --> 21:19.612
LET US REHEARSE, HMM?

21:19.653 --> 21:20.947
EVERYONE, PLEASE...

21:20.988 --> 21:23.407
