OH, I'M SORRY. I'M SORRY.

21:37.504 --> 21:38.798
HELLO? YES.

21:38.839 --> 21:40.841
UH, NO, NO,

21:38.839 --> 21:40.841
I'M IN A REHEARSAL, YES.

