-NO, NO, I UNDERSTAND.

21:40.883 --> 21:43.343
I UNDERSTAND.

21:40.883 --> 21:43.343
[ BEEP ]

21:43.385 --> 21:46.346
I'M SORRY,

21:43.385 --> 21:46.346
BUT THERE'S BEEN AN ACCIDENT

