INVOLVING MY MOTHER

21:46.388 --> 21:49.558
AND A MOPED.

21:49.600 --> 21:51.060
PLEASE, TEMI,

21:49.600 --> 21:51.060
I HAVE READ ABOUT YOU.

21:51.102 --> 21:52.394
I KNOW YOU CAN PLAY THIS

21:51.102 --> 21:52.394
IN YOUR SLEEP,

21:52.436 --> 21:54.147
-SO...

21:52.436 --> 21:54.147
-[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

