...WE WILL SEE YOU

21:54.188 --> 21:56.149
AT THE CONCERT, YES?

21:56.190 --> 21:57.066
YES.

21:57.108 --> 21:58.734
I HOPE YOUR MOTHER IS ALL RIGHT.

