-HOW'S THE PLAN?

22:15.793 --> 22:16.919
-MM.

22:16.961 --> 22:18.712
I'LL WALK YOU THROUGH IT.

22:18.754 --> 22:20.380
WE HAVE THREE MAIN OBSTACLES --

22:20.422 --> 22:21.674
TWO DOORS AND A GUARD.

22:21.715 --> 22:23.759
AT THE FIRST DOOR,

22:21.715 --> 22:23.759
THERE'S A SIX-DIGIT KEYPAD.

22:23.801 --> 22:24.927
YOU GOT THE CODE YET?

22:24.969 --> 22:26.470
LET'S FIND OUT. SOPHIE?

22:28.555 --> 22:30.516
MINUTES AWAY.

22:30.557 --> 22:31.684
OH, MS. CONNELLY, RIGHT?

22:31.725 --> 22:32.810
[ Chuckling ]

22:31.725 --> 22:32.810
OH, YES.

22:32.852 --> 22:34.645
PLEASE, LET ME HELP YOU.

22:34.687 --> 22:36.189
OH! OH [CHUCKLES]

22:34.687 --> 22:36.189
THANK YOU.

22:36.230 --> 22:38.524
YES, I'M HELPING

22:36.230 --> 22:38.524
TO ORGANIZE THE CONCERT,

22:38.565 --> 22:41.027
AND, UM, I JUST WANTED

22:38.565 --> 22:41.027
TO CHECK THE ACOUSTICS,

22:41.068 --> 22:43.403
BECAUSE WE'RE BROADCASTING IT

22:41.068 --> 22:43.403
ON THE RADIO, AND...

22:43.445 --> 22:45.990
WELL, I-I HOPE YOU DON'T MIND.

22:43.445 --> 22:45.990
I HAVE TO CHECK YOUR BAG.

22:46.032 --> 22:47.407
OH, NO, NO, GO AHEAD.

22:47.449 --> 22:49.367
'CAUSE WE'RE ALSO FILMING IT,

22:47.449 --> 22:49.367
FOR TEL-- TELEVISION.

22:49.409 --> 22:51.996
AND THAT LENS -- THAT LENS

22:49.409 --> 22:51.996
IS VERY, VERY SENSITIVE.

22:52.038 --> 22:54.372
PLEASE...PUT IT DOWN GENTLY.

22:54.414 --> 22:55.749
-[ CHUCKLES ]

22:54.414 --> 22:55.749
-I'M SORRY.

22:55.791 --> 22:58.418
THEY'RE VERY, VERY,

22:55.791 --> 22:58.418
VERY FRAGILE.

23:01.505 --> 23:03.174
ALL RIGHT, I'M AT THE DOOR.

23:03.216 --> 23:05.467
[ SPRAYING ]

23:07.511 --> 23:09.972
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

23:10.014 --> 23:11.891
I GOT DOWNSTAIRS.

23:11.932 --> 23:14.227
I -- THEY TOLD ME --

23:11.932 --> 23:14.227
I GOT THE WORK ORDER RIGHT HERE.

23:14.268 --> 23:16.562
NO, NO. WHO AUTHORIZED YOU?

23:16.603 --> 23:20.149
THIS AREA IS FOR

23:16.603 --> 23:20.149
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY!

23:20.191 --> 23:21.567
-LEAVE.

23:20.191 --> 23:21.567
-ALL RIGHT.

23:21.608 --> 23:23.736
-LEAVE.

23:21.608 --> 23:23.736
-I GOTTA CALL MY SUPERVISOR.

23:23.777 --> 23:25.738
YOU KNOW WHAT?

23:23.777 --> 23:25.738
THIS IS TYPICAL. HUH?

23:25.779 --> 23:28.282
HE'S PROBABLY GONNA BLAME IT

23:25.779 --> 23:28.282
ON MY BAD ATTITUDE.

23:28.324 --> 23:30.117
[ KEYPAD BEEPING ]

23:38.458 --> 23:40.794
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

23:40.836 --> 23:43.172
ALL RIGHT,

23:40.836 --> 23:43.172
IT'S A SIX-DIGIT CODE.

23:43.214 --> 23:46.884
THE FIRST TWO NUMBERS

23:43.214 --> 23:46.884
ARE 6 AND 4, IN THAT SEQUENCE.

23:48.510 --> 23:51.471
NEXT FOUR NUMBERS

23:48.510 --> 23:51.471
ARE 2, 3...8, 9...

23:51.513 --> 23:53.891
not in sequence.

23:53.933 --> 23:55.351
OKAY, THAT MEANS

23:55.393 --> 23:56.936
I'M GONNA HAVE TO PUNCH IN

23:55.393 --> 23:56.936
ALL THE COMBINATIONS.

23:56.977 --> 23:58.771
THAT'S GONNA TAKE TIME,

23:56.977 --> 23:58.771
AND THERE'S A GUARD.

23:58.812 --> 24:00.398
WELL, ELIOT CAN TAKE CARE

23:58.812 --> 24:00.398
OF THE GUARD.

24:00.480 --> 24:01.481
Right, Eliot?

24:01.523 --> 24:03.984
YEAH. SURE.

24:04.026 --> 24:05.945
THAT PUTS US

24:04.026 --> 24:05.945
THROUGH THE FIRST DOOR,

24:05.986 --> 24:08.239
AND IT'S A STRAIGHT SHOT

24:05.986 --> 24:08.239
DOWN THROUGH THE STAIRS,

24:08.281 --> 24:10.157
WHICH LEADS US

24:08.281 --> 24:10.157
RIGHT INTO THE VAULT.

24:10.199 --> 24:11.284
WHERE WE HAVE

24:10.199 --> 24:11.284
THE RETINA SCANNER,

24:11.325 --> 24:12.410
WHICH WE DON'T HAVE TIME

24:11.325 --> 24:12.410
TO HACK,

24:12.450 --> 24:13.869
SO I WOULD SKIP THE STAIRS

24:13.911 --> 24:15.579
AND BLOW A HOLE IN THE FLOOR

24:13.911 --> 24:15.579
RIGHT THERE.

24:15.621 --> 24:18.040
OKAY, GREAT, SO --

24:15.621 --> 24:18.040
SO, WE GET TO THE VAULT

24:15.621 --> 24:18.040
THROUGH THE CEILING,

24:18.082 --> 24:19.875
WE GET THE DIAMONDS,

24:18.082 --> 24:19.875
WE WAIT FOR THE CONCERT TO END,

24:19.917 --> 24:21.710
-AND WE SLIP OUT WITH THE CROWD.

24:19.917 --> 24:21.710
-NOPE.

24:21.752 --> 24:24.046
WHAT DO YOU MEAN, "NO"?

24:21.752 --> 24:24.046
THAT'S WHAT YOU JUST --

24:24.088 --> 24:25.756
OUR ONLY WINDOW

24:24.088 --> 24:25.756
TO BREAK INTO THIS VAULT

24:25.798 --> 24:27.800
IS DURING THE CONCERT

24:25.798 --> 24:27.800
WHEN THE MOTION SENSORS

24:25.798 --> 24:27.800
ARE TURNED OFF.

24:27.841 --> 24:29.467
-RIGHT?

24:27.841 --> 24:29.467
-RIGHT.

24:29.509 --> 24:31.637
OKAY, WELL, THIS IS A CONCERT

24:29.509 --> 24:31.637
FOR A FOREIGN DIGNITARY

24:31.678 --> 24:33.139
WITH A FULL

24:31.678 --> 24:33.139
SECRET SERVICE DETAIL.

24:33.180 --> 24:34.598
OKAY, WE HAVE TO

24:33.180 --> 24:34.598
TAKE OUT THE GUARD,

24:34.640 --> 24:37.059
BLOW A HOLE IN THE FLOOR WITHOUT

24:34.640 --> 24:37.059
ANYBODY HEARING ANYTHING.

24:37.101 --> 24:38.476
IT CAN'T BE DONE.

24:38.518 --> 24:40.938
YEAH, I-I CAN'T DO IT,

24:38.518 --> 24:40.938
EITHER, MAN. I'M OUT. MNH-MNH.

24:40.980 --> 24:43.649
YOU KNOW, I'M SORRY

24:40.980 --> 24:43.649
FOR THE PEOPLE OF THIS

24:40.980 --> 24:43.649
COUNTRY -- I REALLY AM --

24:43.690 --> 24:46.319
BUT THIS IS  THE  MOST FRIGHTENING

24:43.690 --> 24:46.319
THING I'VE EVER HAD TO DO.

24:46.360 --> 24:48.279
NO, I'M SORRY, I CAN'T.

24:46.360 --> 24:48.279
MNH-MNH. I'M OUT.

24:48.321 --> 24:50.488
HOW MUCH TIME WE NEED

24:48.321 --> 24:50.488
FOR THE BREAK-IN?

24:50.530 --> 24:51.698
SEVEN MINUTES...

24:51.740 --> 24:53.284
MINIMUM.

24:53.326 --> 24:57.330
SO, HERE'S WHERE ELIOT

24:53.326 --> 24:57.330
TAKES CARE OF THE GUARD,

24:57.371 --> 24:59.623
AND THEN HERE'S WHERE WE BLOW

24:57.371 --> 24:59.623
A HOLE THROUGH THE FLOOR,

24:59.665 --> 25:00.874
THE LAST SEVEN MINUTES

24:59.665 --> 25:00.874
OF THE PIECE,

25:00.916 --> 25:02.209
OF COURSE, DEPENDING ON TEMPO.

