PA-- PARKER,

25:28.277 --> 25:30.446
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

25:30.488 --> 25:31.571
ESTABLISHING MY COVER.

25:31.613 --> 25:32.823
DOING A WALK-THROUGH.

25:31.613 --> 25:32.823
HOW'S IT GOING?

