HOW DO YOU  THINK  IT'S GOING?

25:34.700 --> 25:36.994
IN 24 HOURS, RIGHT WHERE

25:34.700 --> 25:36.994
I'M STANDING, I'M GONNA

25:34.700 --> 25:36.994
MAKE A FOOL OF MYSELF.

