25:42.249 --> 25:44.542
IF YOU CAN'T, THE MARK'S

25:42.249 --> 25:44.542
GONNA KNOW SOMETHING'S UP,

25:44.584 --> 25:45.878
AND THEN HE'S GONNA KILL US ALL.

25:45.919 --> 25:47.004
IS THIS A PEP TALK?

25:47.046 --> 25:48.047
THEN HE'LL TAKE OVER

25:47.046 --> 25:48.047
THE COUNTRY,

25:48.088 --> 25:49.173
ROB HIS PEOPLE BLIND!

25:49.215 --> 25:50.216
I MEAN,

25:49.215 --> 25:50.216
IMAGINE THE SUFFERING --

25:50.257 --> 25:51.884
COME ON, MAN, WITH THE PRESSURE.

25:51.925 --> 25:53.427
I'M JUST TRYING TO GET A LITTLE

25:51.925 --> 25:53.427
ADRENALINE FLOWING HERE.

