IF I GET ADRENALINE FLOWING,

25:56.472 --> 25:59.683
-MY GIANT HANDS ARE GONNA SNAP

25:56.472 --> 25:59.683
THIS PRICELESS VIOLIN IN HALF.

25:56.472 --> 25:59.683
-OH.

25:59.725 --> 26:01.477
YOU'LL BE FINE.

26:35.261 --> 26:36.554
OH, MS. CONNELLY.

26:36.594 --> 26:38.013
ALLOW ME TO INTRODUCE

26:36.594 --> 26:38.013
MY BROTHER,

26:38.055 --> 26:40.182
PRESIDENT SIMEON MOTO.

26:40.224 --> 26:41.517
OH, MR. PRESIDENT,

26:41.559 --> 26:42.684
I THINK YOU'RE GONNA BE

26:41.559 --> 26:42.684
SO  IMPRESSED

26:42.726 --> 26:44.562
WITH WHAT THIS YOUNG MAN

26:42.726 --> 26:44.562
ACHIEVES TONIGHT.

26:44.602 --> 26:46.021
IT WILL BE NICE TO READ

26:44.602 --> 26:46.021
SOMETHING POSITIVE

26:46.063 --> 26:47.856
ABOUT MY COUNTRY FOR A CHANGE.

26:47.898 --> 26:49.233
OH. PLEASE.

27:02.704 --> 27:05.416
