-WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

34:37.659 --> 34:39.494
-I-I'LL EXPLAIN LATER.

34:39.536 --> 34:40.996
LET'S JUST GET OUT OF HERE.

34:41.038 --> 34:42.539
[ ALARM BLARING ]

34:42.581 --> 34:44.290
-YOU GOT AN EXIT PLAN?

34:42.581 --> 34:44.290
-HOLD IT RIGHT THERE.

34:44.332 --> 34:45.834
-AH, WORKING ON IT.

34:45.876 --> 34:47.544
UH, SOPHIE, ANY IDEAS?

34:47.586 --> 34:49.713
[ APPLAUSE ]

34:49.755 --> 34:51.256
STALL.

34:51.297 --> 34:54.467
UH, GUYS,

34:51.297 --> 34:54.467
MOTO AND HIS BROTHER JUST LEFT.

34:54.509 --> 34:56.135
AND I DON'T KNOW ABOUT Y'ALL,

34:54.509 --> 34:56.135
BUT IT WASN'T ME,

34:56.177 --> 34:58.304
'CAUSE, UH, I JUST ROCKED IT,

34:56.177 --> 34:58.304
YOU KNOW.

34:58.346 --> 35:00.599
OKAY, LISTEN, HARDISON,

34:58.346 --> 35:00.599
JUST STAY WHERE YOU ARE

35:00.640 --> 35:01.892
AND DON'T BLOW YOUR COVER.

35:01.934 --> 35:02.976
Roger that.

35:03.018 --> 35:05.270
[ APPLAUSE ]

35:10.108 --> 35:12.151
HOW'S IT GOING?

35:12.193 --> 35:13.820
-WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

35:12.193 --> 35:13.820
-A BURGLARY.

35:13.862 --> 35:17.282
WE TURNED OFF THE MOTION SENSORS

35:13.862 --> 35:17.282
FOR THE CONCERT.

35:17.323 --> 35:18.784
THEY'RE VERY CLEVER.

35:18.825 --> 35:20.702
MY MEN CAN HANDLE IT.

35:22.537 --> 35:23.956
CALL THE POLICE.

35:27.500 --> 35:28.710
YOU SEE?

35:28.752 --> 35:30.754
I TOLD YOU IT WASN'T NECESSARY

35:28.752 --> 35:30.754
TO FOLLOW ME.

35:30.796 --> 35:33.673
YES. YOU DID.

35:33.715 --> 35:36.259
THIS IS WHY YOU CAN NEVER HAVE

35:33.715 --> 35:36.259
TOO MUCH SECURITY.

35:36.301 --> 35:37.469
MR. PRESIDENT, WAIT.

35:39.178 --> 35:41.598
CAN I TELL YOU A STORY ABOUT

35:39.178 --> 35:41.598
YOUR -- YOUR BROTHER HERE

35:41.640 --> 35:44.017
AND HOW HE LURED YOU HERE

35:41.640 --> 35:44.017
TONIGHT TO ASSASSINATE YOU?

35:44.059 --> 35:46.645
OH-HO, THE THIEF SPEAKS!

35:46.686 --> 35:50.983
WHO KNEW WE WOULD BE ENTERTAINED

35:46.686 --> 35:50.983
TWICE TONIGHT?

35:51.024 --> 35:52.985
PLEASE, GO ON.

35:53.026 --> 35:54.319
THINK ABOUT IT.

35:54.360 --> 35:57.656
LAST-MINUTE CONCERT

35:54.360 --> 35:57.656
IN A HALL YOUR BROTHER OWNS,

35:57.697 --> 36:00.366
HIM WAILING

35:57.697 --> 36:00.366
OVER YOUR BLEEDING BODY

36:00.408 --> 36:02.494
LIVE ON THE RADIO,

36:02.535 --> 36:03.787
INSTANTLY BONDING HIMSELF

36:03.829 --> 36:06.539
TO THE THOUSANDS

36:03.829 --> 36:06.539
LISTENING BACK HOME.

36:06.581 --> 36:07.540
[ LAUGHS ]

36:07.582 --> 36:10.376
AND WHO WOULD FOIL THIS PLOT?

36:10.418 --> 36:13.379
YOU  AND YOUR...TEAM

36:10.418 --> 36:13.379
OF BURGLARS?

36:13.421 --> 36:14.547
BURGLARS?

36:14.589 --> 36:16.842
NO, NO, WE'RE NOT IN IT

36:14.589 --> 36:16.842
FOR THE MONEY.

36:16.883 --> 36:19.260
WE WANTED  THIS.

36:19.302 --> 36:20.846
SEE, MR. PRESIDENT,

36:20.887 --> 36:22.764
THIS ENVELOPE CONTAINS THE NAMES

36:20.887 --> 36:22.764
OF TERRORISTS LIVING IN AFRICA

36:22.806 --> 36:27.102
THAT YOUR -- YOUR BROTHER

36:22.806 --> 36:27.102
SUPPLIES US WITH AT HIS LEISURE

36:27.144 --> 36:29.771
FOR A PRICE.

36:29.813 --> 36:33.358
THIS IS WHAT HAPPENS WHEN YOU

36:29.813 --> 36:33.358
PLAY WITH THE C.I.A., MR. MOTO.

36:33.399 --> 36:35.234
WE TAKE WHAT WE NEED.

36:35.276 --> 36:37.112
YOU  CAN'T  BE SERIOUS.

36:37.154 --> 36:38.780
I TURNED A BLIND EYE

36:38.822 --> 36:41.240
TO THESE RUMORS ABOUT YOU

36:38.822 --> 36:41.240
FOR TOO LONG.

36:41.282 --> 36:42.450
THIS IS INSANE!

36:42.492 --> 36:45.370
CAN'T YOU SEE?

36:42.492 --> 36:45.370
HE'S TELLING YOU A STORY!

36:45.411 --> 36:48.373
EVERY DETAIL MORE OUTLANDISH

36:45.411 --> 36:48.373
THAN THE LAST.

36:48.414 --> 36:52.251
IF HE  IS  LYING, THEN GO AHEAD.

36:52.293 --> 36:53.837
OPEN THE ENVELOPE.

36:53.879 --> 36:55.630
YES.

36:55.672 --> 36:57.090
OPEN THE ENVELOPE.

36:58.091 --> 37:00.010
It is  not  what he says.

37:00.052 --> 37:01.553
I  can't  open it.

37:01.594 --> 37:03.013
It doesn't belong to me.

37:03.055 --> 37:05.306
MR. PRESIDENT, THERE'S SOMETHING

37:03.055 --> 37:05.306
YOU SHOULD KNOW.

37:05.348 --> 37:07.642
WE JUST FOUND A RIFLE

37:05.348 --> 37:07.642
IN THE PROJECTION ROOM

37:07.684 --> 37:10.145
WITH A CLEAN PRINT ON THE SCOPE.

37:10.187 --> 37:12.689
THAT LENS -- THAT LENS

37:10.187 --> 37:12.689
IS VERY, VERY, VERY SENSITIVE,

37:12.731 --> 37:14.691
SO IF YOU COULD JUST...

37:25.869 --> 37:28.705
IT WAS MY BROTHER.

37:28.747 --> 37:31.249
-HE IS RESPONSIBLE!

37:28.747 --> 37:31.249
-NO.

37:31.290 --> 37:33.376
NO, I-IT'S --

37:31.290 --> 37:33.376
SHE'S  BEHIND THIS!

37:33.418 --> 37:35.087
-NO, SHE LIED TO ME!

37:33.418 --> 37:35.087
-COME ON!

37:35.128 --> 37:37.714
MY BROTHER'S BEING DUPED

37:35.128 --> 37:37.714
BY THESE THIEVES!

37:48.934 --> 37:51.103
HOW'D YOU KNOW

37:48.934 --> 37:51.103
WHAT WAS IN THE ENVELOPE?

37:51.144 --> 37:52.437
I  DIDN'T.

37:52.478 --> 37:54.606
IT MADE FOR A GOOD STORY,

37:52.478 --> 37:54.606
THOUGH, RIGHT?

37:54.647 --> 37:56.233
SCHEHERAZADE

37:54.647 --> 37:56.233
WOULD HAVE BEEN PROUD.

37:56.315 --> 37:57.692
YEAH. THANK YOU.

38:01.362 --> 38:03.073
YOU DIDN'T OPEN IT.

38:03.115 --> 38:05.242
I DON'T OPEN

38:03.115 --> 38:05.242
OTHER PEOPLE'S MAIL.

38:05.283 --> 38:07.119
IT'S A PRETTY SERIOUS CRIME.

38:09.162 --> 38:10.371
SO YOU OWE ME NOW.

38:10.413 --> 38:12.624
WE HAVE A DEAL --

38:10.413 --> 38:12.624
TO GET MOREAU.

38:12.665 --> 38:16.628
THAT ENVELOPE IS NOT A LINK

38:12.665 --> 38:16.628
IN THE CHAIN TO MOREAU, IS IT?

38:16.669 --> 38:19.505
OTHERWISE, YOU WOULD JUST

38:16.669 --> 38:19.505
HAND IT OVER TO ME RIGHT NOW,

38:16.669 --> 38:19.505
WOULDN'T YOU?

38:19.547 --> 38:22.801
NO, IT'S A LINK

38:19.547 --> 38:22.801
IN THE CHAIN TO  YOU.

38:22.842 --> 38:25.762
THAT'S WHY YOU KNEW

38:22.842 --> 38:25.762
IT WAS IN MOTO'S SAFE...

38:25.804 --> 38:27.806
AND WHAT IT LOOKED LIKE.

38:27.847 --> 38:30.225
YOU SAW HIM PUT IT THERE,

38:27.847 --> 38:30.225
DIDN'T YOU?

38:30.267 --> 38:32.936
MR. FORD,

38:30.267 --> 38:32.936
IN THE SERVICE OF GOOD,

38:32.978 --> 38:35.063
SOMETIMES WE HAVE TO DEAL

38:32.978 --> 38:35.063
WITH BAD PEOPLE

38:35.105 --> 38:36.273
AND DO BAD THINGS.

38:36.314 --> 38:37.440
REALLY?

38:37.482 --> 38:38.775
'CAUSE I WORK WITH A BUNCH

38:37.482 --> 38:38.775
OF BAD GUYS

38:38.817 --> 38:40.610
WHO ARE MORE HONORABLE

38:38.817 --> 38:40.610
THAN YOU WILL EVER BE.

38:40.652 --> 38:42.320
IF WE'RE GONNA HAVE

38:40.652 --> 38:42.320
THIS ARRANGEMENT,

38:42.361 --> 38:44.030
NEVER PLAY ME AGAIN.

38:48.868 --> 38:50.870
I  STILL  CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

38:50.912 --> 38:53.165
MY ARTICLE IS FINALLY PUBLISHED,

38:53.206 --> 38:54.415
AND THE LEAD IS,

38:54.457 --> 38:57.418
"ALEXANDER MOTO

38:54.457 --> 38:57.418
IS IN AN AMERICAN JAIL."

38:57.460 --> 38:59.796
YES, WELL, IT TURNED OUT

38:57.460 --> 38:59.796
THAT THE SECRET SERVICE

38:59.838 --> 39:01.256
DID NOT TAKE KINDLY TO PEOPLE

39:01.298 --> 39:03.758
TRYING TO ASSASSINATE

39:01.298 --> 39:03.758
FOREIGN LEADERS ON THEIR WATCH.

39:03.800 --> 39:07.428
BUT, MR. FORD,

39:03.800 --> 39:07.428
THAT IS JUST A STORY, RIGHT?

39:07.470 --> 39:10.140
WELL, RIGHT, I MEAN, YEAH,

39:07.470 --> 39:10.140
THE CHARGES AREN'T GONNA STICK.

39:10.182 --> 39:12.809
BUT IT WAS ENOUGH TO GET

39:10.182 --> 39:12.809
A WARRANT TO SEARCH HIS VAULT,

39:12.851 --> 39:14.978
WHICH TURNED UP A MESS

39:12.851 --> 39:14.978
OF SMUGGLED DIAMONDS.

39:15.020 --> 39:16.188
AND THE FACT IS,

39:16.229 --> 39:17.814
HE'S  NEVER

39:16.229 --> 39:17.814
GONNA BE PRESIDENT NOW.

39:17.856 --> 39:19.316
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

39:19.398 --> 39:22.194
WE, UH, WE HAVE THIS FOR YOU.

39:24.154 --> 39:25.655
NO, NO.

39:25.697 --> 39:27.699
THE DIAMONDS...

39:27.740 --> 39:30.160
HAVE NOTHING TO DO WITH THAT.

39:30.202 --> 39:32.704
NO, SEE,

39:30.202 --> 39:32.704
WHAT HAPPENED IS, WE...

39:32.745 --> 39:34.580
WE ENDED UP

39:32.745 --> 39:34.580
WITH THIS STRADIVARIUS.

39:34.622 --> 39:37.000
WE THOUGHT THAT THE MONEY COULD

39:34.622 --> 39:37.000
BE USED FOR THE GOOD PEOPLE

39:34.622 --> 39:37.000
OF WADATA,

39:37.042 --> 39:38.668
MAYBE A MUSIC FOUNDATION

39:37.042 --> 39:38.668
FOR THE KIDS?

39:40.586 --> 39:42.547
YOU COULD SET THAT UP.

39:42.588 --> 39:45.466
IT WAS  HIS  IDEA.

39:52.974 --> 39:55.060
STILL, I WISH WE COULD DO MORE.

39:55.101 --> 39:57.937
WHAT IS IT

39:55.101 --> 39:57.937
YOUR FRIEND SAID TO MOTO?

39:57.979 --> 40:00.857
HELP A SINGLE CHILD,

39:57.979 --> 40:00.857
YOU ARE A HERO?

40:02.234 --> 40:06.071
SMALL ACTS

40:02.234 --> 40:06.071
CAN HAVE RIPPLE EFFECTS.

40:09.574 --> 40:12.827
YOU HAD A RECORDING OF THE SOLO

40:09.574 --> 40:12.827
IN A GIZMO.

40:12.869 --> 40:14.412
THAT MADE IT COME OUT

40:12.869 --> 40:14.412
OF THE VIOLIN.

40:14.453 --> 40:16.122
NO. NO, PARKER.

40:16.164 --> 40:20.210
YOU DON'T JUST JAM A GIZMO

40:16.164 --> 40:20.210
INTO A STRAD, OKAY?

40:20.252 --> 40:23.004
I JUST -- I LET IT RIP.

40:23.046 --> 40:24.422
IT WAS --

40:24.463 --> 40:26.758
WELL, I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE

40:24.463 --> 40:26.758
YOU CAN PLAY LIKE THAT.

40:26.799 --> 40:27.926
YOU?

40:26.799 --> 40:27.926
I  CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

40:27.967 --> 40:30.720
IT'S BECAUSE I HYPNOTIZED YOU.

40:31.804 --> 40:33.098
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:34.640 --> 40:36.059
YOU SERIOUS?

40:36.101 --> 40:38.186
YEAH, I-I PUT YOU

40:36.101 --> 40:38.186
IN A DEEP-TRANCE STATE

40:38.228 --> 40:40.063
AND REGRESSED YOU

40:40.105 --> 40:41.480
BACK TO WHEN YOU PLAYED VIOLIN

40:40.105 --> 40:41.480
AS A TEENAGER.

40:41.522 --> 40:43.108
I MEAN, YOU KNEW

40:41.522 --> 40:43.108
HOW TO PLAY IT ALL ALONG,

40:43.149 --> 40:45.651
BUT I-I CLEANED OUT THE COBWEBS.

40:45.693 --> 40:47.486
I JUST GAVE YOU THE CONFIDENCE

40:47.528 --> 40:51.366
TO BE THE BEST VERSION OF YOU

40:47.528 --> 40:51.366
I KNEW YOU COULD BE.

40:51.408 --> 40:52.867
YOU ARE NOW BACK TO WHEN

40:52.909 --> 40:55.328
YOU WERE THE MOST PROMISING

40:52.909 --> 40:55.328
YOUNG VIOLINIST IN THE CITY

40:55.370 --> 40:57.163
AT THE HEIGHT OF YOUR ABILITIES.

40:57.205 --> 40:59.624
WHAT WAS THE LAST PIECE

40:57.205 --> 40:59.624
YOU PLAYED?

40:59.665 --> 41:01.960
"SCHEHERAZADE."

41:02.001 --> 41:03.420
WHAT WERE YOU DOING UP THERE?

41:02.001 --> 41:03.420
NAPPING?

41:03.461 --> 41:04.963
I TOLD YOU --

41:03.461 --> 41:04.963
WE GOT LOTS OF WORK TO DO.

41:05.004 --> 41:06.672
IS THERE ANYTHING

41:05.004 --> 41:06.672
YOU WANT TO TELL ME?

41:06.714 --> 41:08.049
YOU SAID IT YOURSELF.

41:08.091 --> 41:10.385
HE'S THE BEST CANDIDATE.

41:10.427 --> 41:12.845
A VEGAS HYPNOTIST

41:12.887 --> 41:14.931
CAN PICK OUT A CANDIDATE

41:12.887 --> 41:14.931
IN A CROWD,

41:14.973 --> 41:17.225
AND...SO CAN I.

41:19.769 --> 41:21.271
NATE...

41:21.313 --> 41:24.023
HYPNOSIS IS SOMETHING YOU DO

41:21.313 --> 41:24.023
TO A MARK,

41:24.065 --> 41:25.317
NOT YOUR OWN CREW.

41:25.358 --> 41:26.776
NO, NO, NO.

41:26.818 --> 41:28.653
IT'S  EXACTLY  WHAT YOU DO

41:26.818 --> 41:28.653
TO YOUR OWN CREW.

41:28.694 --> 41:31.156
YEAH, YOU PUSH WHATEVER BUTTON

41:28.694 --> 41:31.156
YOU NEED TO

41:31.197 --> 41:33.658
TO GET THEM TO DO

41:31.197 --> 41:33.658
WHAT NEEDS TO BE DONE.

41:33.699 --> 41:36.369
YOU WANTED TO KNOW

41:33.699 --> 41:36.369
WHAT OTHER QUALITY

41:36.411 --> 41:38.830
YOU NEEDED

41:36.411 --> 41:38.830
TO RUN YOUR OWN CREW.

41:38.871 --> 41:41.707
WELL, THAT'S IT.

41:38.871 --> 41:41.707
AND YOU DON'T HAVE IT.

41:43.960 --> 41:45.628
[ KNOCKS ON COUNTER ]

41:56.264 --> 41:58.308
ALONE AGAIN.

41:58.350 --> 42:00.643
IF I DIDN'T KNOW YOU BETTER,

42:00.685 --> 42:03.396
I'D THINK YOU LIKE IT

42:00.685 --> 42:03.396
LIKE THAT.

42:03.438 --> 42:06.191
[ FOOTSTEPS DEPARTING ]

42:06.232 --> 42:08.485
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]
